 Stadium]]\n|competitors = 13\n|nations = 8\n|win_label = Winning distance\n|win_value = 21.16 ''{{OlyR|athletics}}''\n|longnames = yes\n|gold = [[Ivanka Khristova]]\n|goldNOC = BUL\n|silver = [[Nadezhda Chizhova]]\n|silverNOC = URS\n|bronze = [[Helena Fibingerov\u00e1]]\n|bronzeNOC = TCH\n|prev = [[Athletics at the 1972 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's shot put|1972]]\n|next = [[Athletics at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's shot put|1980]]\n}}\n{{AthleticsAt1976SummerOlympics}}\nThe '''[[Shot put|women's shot put]]''' event at the [[Athletics at the 1976 Summer Olympics|1976 Summer Olympics]] in [[Montreal, Quebec]], Canada had an entrylist of 13 competitors. The final was held on 31 July 1976. There was no qualification round.<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1976/ATH/womens-shot-put.html |title=Athletics at the 1976 Montreal Summer Games: Women's Shot Put |accessdate=8 January 2018 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==Medalists==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|- \n|{{OlympicGoldMedalist|[[Ivanka Khristova]]|BUL|1976 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicSilverMedalist|[[Nadezhda Chizhova]]|URS|1976 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicBronzeMedalist|[[Helena Fibingerov\u00e1]]|TCH|1976 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Abbreviations==\n*''All results shown are in metres''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"ccffcc\"| '''Q''' || automatic qualification\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"ddffdd\"| '''q''' || qualification by rank\n|-\n|'''DNS''' || did not start\n|-\n|'''NM''' || no mark\n|-\n|'''OR''' || olympic record\n|-\n|'''WR''' || world record\n|-\n|'''AR''' || area record\n|-\n|'''NR''' || national record\n|-\n|'''PB''' || personal best\n|-\n|'''SB''' || season best\n|}\n\n==Records==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"95%\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"5\"|Standing records prior to the 1976 Summer Olympics\n|-\n| [[